  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study to collect information on the safety, especially serious infections
      and malignancies, and efficacy of the long-term use of ORENCIA Intravenous Infusion 250mg in
      patients with rheumatoid arthritis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
